<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 602px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #4537de;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(35, 51, 64, 0.25);
        }
        .column-1 {
            float: left;
            width: 400px;
            height: 200px;
            border-right: 2px dashed #fff;
        }
        .column-2 {
            float: right;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
        }
        .text-frame {
            padding: 40px;
            height: 120px;
        }
        .qr-holder {
            position: relative;
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 30px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .qr-holder > img {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .event {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .date {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 30px;
            color: #a8bbf8;
        }
        .name,
        .ticket-id {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 22px;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Reservation Number : {{ id }}</h1>
<p>Thank you for choosing to book with Joy Travel.</p>
<p>We look forward to welcoming you on the {{ dateArrivee | date('Y-m-d')}} </p>
<p>Our professional and friendly staff are committed to ensuring your stay is both enjoyable and comfortable.</p>
<p>Should you have any requests prior to your stay, please do not hesitate to contact us and we will endeavor to assist you whenever possible.</p>
<p>Thanks & Best Regards</p>
<p>The Joy Travel , Fill your Soul !</p>
</body>
</html>